#### Steps to reproduce the behaviour
1. Run a monkey test with this command:

```sh
adb shell monkey -p org.gnucash.android -v -s 1234 --ignore-security-exceptions --kill-process-after-error --monitor-native-crashes 100000
```

#### Expected behaviour

App shouldn't crash

#### Actual behaviour

